Resume evidence: "Senior Architect at Acme from 2020 to 2024; led cloud migration and microservices redesign"
Output: {"extracted":{"experience_entries":[{"period":"2020-2024","organisation":"Acme","responsibilities":["Led cloud migration","Redesigned microservices"]}]}}

Example 4 - no safe evidence
Input field: {"name":"availability","field_type":"scalar"}
Resume evidence: none
Output: {"extracted":{"availability":""}}

